TITLE: Using Formatting Helpers in Telegraf for Text Styling
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use the new formatting helpers to style text without manual escaping. The example demonstrates bold, italic, mention, and link formatting using template literals with the fmt function.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.10.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
import { fmt, bold, italics, mention } from "telegraf/format";

ctx.reply(fmt`
Ground control to ${mention("Major Tom", 10000000)}
${bold`Lock your Soyuz hatch`} and ${italic`put your helmet on`}
â€” ${link("David Bowie", "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Bowie")}
`);
```

