TITLE: Implementing Default Session in Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the new way to set up default session values using the defaultSession parameter instead of a separate middleware. This approach is cleaner and more efficient for initializing session data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.12.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// ðŸ¤¢ Old way
bot.use(session());
bot.use((ctx, next) => {
  ctx.session ??= { count: 0 };
  return next();
});

// ðŸ˜ New way âœ…
bot.use(session({ defaultSession: () => ({ count: 0 }) }));
```

