TITLE: Using Composer.reaction for Handling Emoji Reactions in Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to listen for the addition and removal of emoji reactions using Composer.reaction. The handler can detect both standard emoji and custom emoji reactions identified by their IDs.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.16.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
bot.reaction("ðŸ‘", (ctx) => {
  // user added a ðŸ‘ reaction
});

// prefix with - to listen to reaction removal
bot.reaction("-ðŸ‘", (ctx) => {
  // user removed a ðŸ‘ reaction
});
```

