TITLE: Command Argument Parsing in Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to access parsed command arguments using ctx.args, ctx.command, and ctx.payload in command handlers. Demonstrates the new command parsing functionality.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.13.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// User sends /warn --delete "Offtopic chat"

bot.command("warn", async ctx => {
  ctx.args; // [ "--delete", "Offtopic chat" ]

  ctx.command; // [ "warn" ]
  ctx.payload; // "--delete \"Offtopic chat\""
});
```

