TITLE: Mixed Filter Arrays in Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use arrays of mixed update types and filters for both bot.on and ctx.has methods.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.11.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
// match a message update or a callbackQuery with data present
bot.on(["message", callbackQuery("data")], handler);

if (ctx.has(["message", callbackQuery("data")])) {
  // ctx.update is a message update or a callbackQuery with data present
};
```

