TITLE: Using Formatting Helpers with Photo Captions in Telegraf
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the formatting helpers with photo captions, showing that the formatting system works seamlessly with media captions as well as regular text messages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.10.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: TypeScript
CODE:
```
ctx.replyWithPhoto(
  file.id,
  { caption: fmt`${bold`File name:`} ${file.name}` },
);
```

