TITLE: Importing New Middleware in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to import the new useNewReplies middleware, which changes the behavior of Context::reply* methods to reply to the context message.
SOURCE: https://github.com/telegraf/telegraf/blob/v4/release-notes/4.9.0.md#2025-04-19_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
